557
00:48:16,580 --> 00:48:18,940
I'm sorry, but I can't.

558
00:48:18,940 --> 00:48:22,680
I have nothing to do with that person.

559
00:48:53,210 --> 00:48:57,320
Ahjummeoni, the ant traps that are

560
00:48:58,120 --> 00:49:01,590
in the corners...

561
00:49:05,090 --> 00:49:07,430
Ahjummeoni,

562
00:49:07,430 --> 00:49:10,900
over here, please. Let me explain.

563
00:49:11,830 --> 00:49:15,500
The ant traps,

564
