570
00:50:43,790 --> 00:50:45,690
Is it you, Honey?

571
00:51:07,250 --> 00:51:09,250
Are you Chi Hyeon?

572
00:51:11,650 --> 00:51:13,720
Who are you?

573
00:51:14,850 --> 00:51:16,920
