574
00:51:34,610 --> 00:51:36,610
Are you looking for this?

575
00:51:38,580 --> 00:51:40,350
Father.

576
00:51:42,210 --> 00:51:44,020
Are you Joon Jae?

577
00:51:48,790 --> 00:51:51,720
What were you doing in here?

578
00:51:51,720 --> 00:51:53,830
Are you really Joon Jae?

579
00:51:53,830 --> 00:51:59,460
What in the world are you seeing in here?!

580
00:52:01,530 --> 00:52:04,440
What's with you?

581
00:52:04,440 --> 00:52:06,370
You couldn't even recognize your own son.

582
00:52:07,720 --> 00:52:10,740
To suffer into this state,
you separated from my mom

583
00:52:12,040 --> 00:52:14,550
and you treated me so badly?

584
00:52:23,420 --> 00:52:27,630
Oh, Ahjumma, Ahjumma! Would you look over here?

585
00:52:27,630 --> 00:52:31,760
Underneath this carpet, usually...

586
00:52:31,760 --> 00:52:32,700
Let me just go to the room for a second.

587
00:52:32,700 --> 00:52:36,940
Oh, Ahjumma! You need to hear more.

588
00:52:45,140 --> 00:52:46,850
Let's leave for now.

589
00:52:46,850 --> 00:52:47,580
To where?

590
00:52:47,580 --> 00:52:49,580
Anywhere but this house.

591
00:52:49,580 --> 00:52:51,020
Yeah, but why?

592
00:52:51,020 --> 00:52:54,390
If you stay here any longer,
we won't know what will happen to you.

593
00:52:54,390 --> 00:52:59,060
This is my house.
What would happen to me in my own house?

594
00:53:00,430 --> 00:53:08,400
What happened to Manager Nam, and to
