595
00:53:09,530 --> 00:53:14,770
I don't know how you entered into this house, but...

596
00:53:14,770 --> 00:53:19,540
After coming back home after ten years, all
you can do is choose to slander your mother?

597
00:53:19,540 --> 00:53:21,750
Who's my mother?

598
00:53:21,750 --> 00:53:27,890
You probably wanted to tell
me that my choice was wrong.

599
00:53:27,890 --> 00:53:31,820
Yes, you chose wrong.

600
00:53:31,820 --> 00:53:33,090
From the beginning to the end. Everything!

601
00:53:33,090 --> 00:53:36,090
