602
00:53:36,090 --> 00:53:41,000
It's my choice! And it's my life! It's not wrong.

603
00:53:41,000 --> 00:53:43,170
I was happy.

604
00:53:44,670 --> 00:53:47,940
Just because my eyesight is getting a bit dull,

605
00:53:47,940 --> 00:53:53,880
