better after surgery.

607
00:54:00,190 --> 00:54:03,990
It's because my body's condition isn't good that
I can't do surgery. If I just did surgery...!

608
00:54:03,990 --> 00:54:08,530
It seems that I, who am standing in front
of you, am the only one you can't see.

609
00:54:08,530 --> 00:54:11,530
You can't see anything.

610
00:54:11,530 --> 00:54:15,330
How your life is going downhill...

611
00:54:16,870 --> 00:54:19,600
