624
00:55:14,090 --> 00:55:18,560
Even if by force, I have to take you with me.

625
00:55:18,560 --> 00:55:20,370
Let's go.

626
00:55:21,170 --> 00:55:22,870
Let's go.

627
00:55:22,870 --> 00:55:27,540
Let me go! He said you've been defrauding people!

628
00:55:27,540 --> 00:55:33,380
That's why you're doing this horrible
thing to me now, you bastard!

629
00:55:49,290 --> 00:55:52,000
(I called) because it's weird with
the loud noises from upstairs.

630
00:55:52,000 --> 00:55:55,070
They said they work for an
exterminator company but

631
00:55:55,070 --> 00:55:57,670
